# VHS tape for the README demo — https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# Regenerate with:  vhs docs/demo.tape   (from the repo root)
Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 900
Set Height 280
Set Padding 16
Set Framerate 24
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "./docs/demo_sim.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 15s
